jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">3. Local news</p>\r\n<p id=\"a0bc\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">There are two English speaking newspapers in Dubai:</p>\r\n<p id=\"1dac\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">●&nbsp;<a class=\"bz do jf jg jh ji\" href=\"http://www.gulf-news.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">www.gulf-news.com</a></p>\r\n<p id=\"b1a8\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">●&nbsp;<a class=\"bz do jf jg jh ji\" href=\"http://www.khaleejtimes.com/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">www.khaleejtimes.com</a></p>\r\n<p id=\"a0ab\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\"><strong class=\"ij jj\">Emergency numbers</strong></p>\r\n<p id=\"e051\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Police &mdash; 999 (from anywhere in the UAE)</p>\r\n<p id=\"13e1\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Ambulance &mdash; 998</p>\r\n<p id=\"d0f3\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Fire &mdash; 997</p>\r\n<p id=\"fd3f\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Dubai Police Call Centre &mdash; 901</p>\r\n<p id=\"6715\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb jc jd je gi cr\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\">Dubai Police (non-emergency) &mdash; 04&ndash;609 6999</p>\r\n<p id=\"2256\" class=\"ih ii gq ij b ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja j