(40, 0, 'geo-fencing-notifications.jpg', 'geo-fencing-notifications', 4, 9, 'Geo Fencing', '2020-12-10 13:21:55', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p><strong>Push Notification Mobile Phone Advertising Services Dubai UAE</strong></p>\r\n<p>This format has traditionally worked very well for advertisers because it allows the user to see and interact with the ad at a time that suits them. Unlike traditional ads, which disappear after a few seconds or minutes, notification ads allow the user to interact with the ad at a time convenient to them. A push ad can stay in the notification tray for several hours, so the user can view and interact with the ad when it\'s relevant to them.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What are push notifications?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Push notification is a pop-up message on a mobile device. App publishers can submit it at any time; Users do not need to be in the application or use their device to receive them. They can do a lot; For example, they can view the latest sports scores, call the user, such as download a coupon, or notify the user of an event, such as a quick sale.</p>\r\n<p>Push notifications look like text and mobile alerts, with push notification support on every mobile platform - iOS, Android, Fire OS, Windows and Blackberry all have their services.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why is push notification a good idea for you?</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Send an ad even if the customer is not using the site or app.</li>\r\n<li>Connect with customers, don\'t panic</li>\r\n<li>Send relevant and timely messages for a strong conversion.</li>\r\n<li>It can be accessed on all devices</li>\r\n<li>Make A / B testing easy by optimizing creative images and ad content.</li>\r\n<li>Provide statistics to instantly improve your campaign</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>How they work?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Push notifications are a well-known and used marketing tool that helps re-share apps on a user\'s device. These ads are an important source of revenue for app developers and site owners, as they allow inactive users to monetize. According to data from the Localytics data team, app sharing through push notifications increases by 88%. They also found that 50% of users would prefer to subscribe to informational information and find it useful for their user experience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It\'s not well known that advertisers of all types, including brands, direct response, user acquisition, original content, and search content, have used high visibility, click, and overall performance statements. Push notifications provide a high level of resilience and engagement, and help increase your overall return on investment.</p>\r\n<p>Traditional image ads can only be seen when a user opens an application or visits a domain, but informational messages allow you to increase your chances of making money from inactive users while the ads run on the device itself. .</p>\r\n<p>There are several versions of the distribution available to display user information. Most users may not be aware of this, as the user experience will remain the same in all versions of push notifications.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Application developers can provide push notifications to their users through the SDK</li>\r\n<li>Website owners use Chrome to send notifications to the user on the device</li>\r\n<li>Manufacturers (OEMs) and mobile operators (telecommunications) also send push notifications to their users</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Why ImranOnline?</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Targeting - Geographic Fence</li>\r\n<li>Choice Data - Provides highly accurate real-time GPS positioning</li>\r\n<li>Polygons are easily targeted to active users in any geographic area</li>\r\n<li>Campaigns are able to display different designs and prices for different polygons</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Display Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Text Push: Advertisement Title 25 characters &ndash; Ad Body&nbsp; text 40 characters &ndash; Logo 72x72px 50Kb</li>\r\n<li>Banner Push Notification: 728x90px JPG &ndash; 50Kb Maximum File Size</li>\r\n<li>Big Pictur: 400x250px PNG/JPG &ndash; 150Kb Maximum File Size 96x96px PNG/JPG Logo &ndash; 50Kb&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Offer Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Destination URL (Click Trackers)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Product Requirements:&nbsp; Source Files such as Photoshop and Illustrator</strong></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', 'aqsVpPmOt', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-05 04:28:22', 0),
(4, 1, 'seach-engine-optimization.jpg', 'seach-engine-optimization', 17, 1, 'Seach Engine Optimization', '2020-12-10 20:28:16', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">To design, develop and host business or personal website is not enough to succeed online. To ensure its presence over the first page of popular search engines like Google, Bing, Baidu and Yandex you need the services of certified, experienced and professional digital marketing company that can help you to ensure your presence over internet. It is best to hire search engines optimization or SEO to get high rankings in search engines as well as get high quality traffic to your site. Well, it is clear that only an SEO services expert can advertise your business in the internet world and show it to the target customers. Therefore, you should hire the professional SEO Company for this job. However, it is also imperative to choose the best SEO Company to get the most profit. Therefore, when setting up an SEO service for your business, keep a few good points in mind.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><sup><strong>1st</strong> </sup>Do You Research First: Do your homework before hiring the services of SEO Company. Read basic SEO services, and once you are well versed in SEO objectives, facts and practices, you can better judge the expertise of SEO Company. Therefore, you can discuss the services they provide well before hiring them.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><sup>2nd</sup></strong> Evaluate the different SEO packages: Frankly speaking, a right and professional SEO service provider will perform some of the best SEO techniques such as on page and off page site analysis, pre-optimization, keyword research, social advertising and more. If you find a package that offers these SEO services, you can hire SEO package for long-term or short-term basis. SEO companies offer