llusion you want to create to attract the audience\'s attention, our video experts will do it for you.&nbsp; Our talents and support are available to us through technology. We use our artistic and creative minds to provide our audience with an inspiring and memorable experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect Motion Graphics</strong></p>\r\n<p>Design a digital footage and animation combine to give you exciting new ways to present your ideas to audiences around the world. Multimedia is the future of corporate video production. Stay ahead of the crowd. The animations we offer to our customers are designed to make an impression. Whether it\'s the corporate videos, events or presentations you want to use, our animations will leave your audience appealing. Make a lasting impression on your audience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Script Writing</strong></p>\r\n<p>Great stories come from great writing. We think more about developing an audio script that reaches your audience and speaks to the words they associate with. It helps clients communicate with their audience and cultivate intimate relationships. Screenwriting is an essential aspect of our video production services. Whether you want to submit a feedback video or a full animation, we will get your lesson for the first time. Corporate videos don\'t have to be the same in the UAE.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Virtual reality - interactive</strong></p>\r\n<p>In an age where technology is evolving at an unprecedented rate, virtual reality has emerged as a vehicle for stories that immerse viewers\' minds with amazing experiences. We use our animation technologies mixed with programming to create an interactive experience for a lifetime. Storytelling is the cornerstone of our value proposition.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Strong customer feedback in high quality video production</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Creativity, quality and technical competence</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>IMRANONLINE</strong> provides digital services to more than 100 Fortune companies with extensive experience in video production and advertising. With great customer feedback, it is one of the most popular brands in video creation and editing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', 'CZEAacrZC', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-05 05:12:18', 0),
(28, 0, 'youtube-advertising-dubai.jpg', 'youtube-advertising-dubai', 4, 0, 'YouTube Advertising Dubai', '2020-12-10 13:49:15', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>YouTube is one of the social media giants with more than 3 billion users. We are a Certified Google Partner ready to help you advertise on YouTube. Video ads run on YouTube, and you only pay when people watch your video ads. Online video advertising is a great way to introduce you to potential customers. Get started with online video advertising campaigns today. In video ads, your business appears in front of the people you want to reach, and you only pay when they see them.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>YouTube Advertising Agency</strong></p>\r\n<p>With over 3 billion video views a day and over 72 hours of content every minute, YouTube is without a doubt an online video streaming site. YouTube has millions of fans who could be potential customers if they were targeted. Their huge audience base is the biggest reason why companies use this platform to run targeted video advertising campaigns. YouTube, the largest video-sharing site, gives businesses the opportunity to showcase their product videos and gain leads.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To see where everyone is looking</strong></p>\r\n<p>With the TrueView for Action campaign, you can reach potential customers when they watch or search for videos on YouTube, and pay only when they\'re interested.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Focus on high quality videos that fit your budget</strong></p>\r\n<p>Learn how to create an attractive promotional video over the phone or professionally.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Find the right story for your business</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bring your experience, passion and story to life. Here are some examples to help you think about your promotional video.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reach the people that have values for you&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>You don\'t have to show your ad to everyone - only those who are interested in what you have to offer. Fashion lovers around the world all are on YouTube.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Think about what you want to deliver</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Select people based on location, age, interests, and more.</strong></p>\r\n<p>With YouTube ads, you can choose who is in your video ads</p>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Where is your customer located?</strong></p>\r\n<p>You can show video ads for the entire country or for just one city, or a combination of both, near or around the world.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Demographics</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Who is your customer?</strong></p>\r\n<p>You Tuber viewers come from all walks of life. Think about your customers\' age, gender, parental status and family income.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Interests</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>What is your customer interest?</strong></p>\r\n<p>You will be able to choose from more than 100 interests to reduce the interest of specific customers. Match and align interests to optimize access.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Review the types of ads you can run</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Choose between long or short video ads</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tell your story in six or sixty seconds, and we\'ll show it to the right people, no matter where they look.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reach a captive audience before watching a video</strong></p>\r\n<p>TrueView in-stream ads Your company\'s video ads appear in front of the right people before the main video is viewed.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When customers search for videos, they appear</strong></p>\r\n<p>TrueView in-search ads appear on the YouTube homepage or when users search YouTube. Use this format when comparing search queries to refine your report.</p>\r\n<p><strong>A short video ad that\'s perfect for your smartphone</strong></p>\r\n<p>The wings are only 6 seconds. This is a good way to get people\'s attention on your smartphone. Use it alone or in conjunction with a TrueView campaign.</p>\r\n<p><strong>You will only pay them if:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>It monitors your ad for 30 seconds</li>\r\n<li>Your ad is fully monitored</li>\r\n<li>Clicks on your ad</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Get real-time insight into how people respond to your video ads. So you know how to do it - and how to do it better.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>YouTube Advertising Opportunities</strong></p>\r\n<p>YouTube has more than 1 billion users and is the largest video site on the Internet. Because the video is distributed on other social platforms, YouTube advertising is a must if you want to display high quality video content.</p>\r\n<p>However, YouTube\'s best strategy can\'t be implemented without the best content, and the first five seconds of advertising are the most important time to get a user\'s attention to connect. We can provide suggestions on what kind of content attracts your target users the most and what your competitors are creating.</p>\r\n<p>There are two main forms of YouTube advertising:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>TrueView In-stream Ad</strong> - Shows all video ad campaigns you started before other videos or in longer video locations.</li>\r\n<li><strong>TrueView Discovery</strong> - It uses banners and thumbnails of traditional ad formats to entice users to click on a video or website.</li>\r\n<li><strong>TrueView for Shopping</strong> - These campaigns provide more information by targeting your products directly to your products, bringing customers closer to your purchase.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>YouTube ads can appear on YouTube searches and YouTube videos, including Google partner sites, apps, and the Google Display Network.</p>\r\n<p>To ensure that your ads reach the appropriate user, we can target users with a number of options: behavior, interests, remarketing, placements, and keywords.</p>\r\n<p>We\'ll review your overall marketing strategy and business goals to determine how to maximize YouTube ads to drive that strategy.</p>\r\n<p><strong>YouTube text and banner ads, various elements of online marketing that we can support, include:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Google Text AdWords</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>You only pay for users who click on your site and visit</li>\r\n<li>We will create and manage campaigns. The campaign will be monitored regularly and adjusted accordingly to achieve the best results.</li>\r\n<li>We will report periodically.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>YouTube video ad campaign</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cost-per-view (CPM)</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>CPV bidding is the default way to set a reasonable price for your AdWords for video ads. Although regular image ads charge for impressions, cost-per-view is only paid when the viewer watches your video.</li>\r\n<li>With traditional text ads or online image ads, customers can view your ad on the web, read its text, and click on your URL to go directly to their site. Interactions such as video ads are not considered in such interactions. With CPM bidding, your ad will not be clicked on any impressions or video interactions.</li>\r\n<li>With the AdWords for video report, you can measure how much your audience interacts with your content, where they choose to watch your video, and when they leave your content.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', 'PRijCwAHZ', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-05 05:13:56', 0),
(1, 1, 'website-development-38.jpg', 'website-development', 23, 8, 'Website Development', '2020-12-10 20:16:58', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>Every site owner needs the professional web development services as per your requirements. The online world and digital marketing services are changing frequently and rapidly, so keeping up with the latest trend is an important aspect. Unless your company is in the web development industry, you have to hire the services of a certified, experienced and certified web development services.</p>\r\n<p>Today, to outsource web development services will greatly influence your business objectives, goals, strategies and profit. The custom designed web development services provide a great way to maximize profits with an affordable investment. In the outsourcing website development competition, there are countless and world-class IT services. it is the fact that the best website development companies are ruled by a custom designed service, dedication, innovative and skilled website developer. The website development services provider who have knowledge of technologies like PHP, Joomla, ASP.NET, Java that are needed to create a personalized, innovative, interactive, responsive and friendly website.</p>\r\n<h2>These are the top tips that are necessary to consider whiling outsourcing your website development services.</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Responsive Customer Service</strong>: The web development activity will involve ongoing collaboration with the website development services provider, that why it is mandatory to website development company to provide a high level of customer service. You should check the company\'s previous customer feedback and make sure that they have a team of responsive and dedicated customer service.&nbsp; The company should have a good customer service history. Before hiring any website company, it is recommended to hold a face-to-face meeting with website development repr