(2, 1, 'e-commerce-solutions.jpg', 'e-commerce-solutions', 4, 0, 'E-commerce Solutions', '2020-12-10 19:35:42', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>The e-commerce industry is booming and customers are introduced to many online stores. Competition has reached a high level as developers optimize e-commerce solutions and integrate advanced technologies and features such as AR, VR and IoT.</p>\r\n<p>E-commerce store owners are constantly striving to develop rich features and attractive digital catalogs, but store owners lack a specific point in the strategic process and forget that an effective development process alone is not enough.</p>\r\n<p>E-commerce markets are growing at a significant pace. The internet market is expected to grow by 56% between 2015 and 2020. In 2017, e-retail worldwide reached $ 2.3 trillion, and e-retail revenue is expected to grow to $ 4.88 trillion in 2021.</p>\r\n<p>Therefore, e-commerce must be updated with new features and functionalities. The development and launch process doesn\'t end there. Maintenance plays an important role. So in this article today, we will share with you some of the ecommerce development services that online stores need to improve the revenue process.</p>\r\n<h2>Ways to increase your ecommerce sales</h2>\r\n<h3>Custom e-commerce development</h3>\r\n<p>One size does not fit all. There are certain requirements for each e-commerce store. In such cases, the development of custom e-commerce involves the development of solutions based on user requirements, the latest trends, as well as business needs using up-to-date tools and technologies.</p>\r\n<h3>Subject Development Service</h3>\r\n<p>Improved appearance and design are used to launch from time to time. It is important that you maintain a standard and distinct presence on the digital platform. Your underlying item should not be out of date or of interest. The theme reflects your style, so work on it at a specific time and turn it into s