ls contact to&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #626262; font-weight: bold;\">IMRNAONLINE</span>&nbsp;responsive and friendly staff. Let&rsquo;s grow your e-commerce online business with the help of custom designed <strong>IMRNAONLINE</strong> e-commerce solutions.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', 'NsuAGpqOb', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-10 23:20:04', 0),
(44, 0, 'smart-solutions.jpg', 'smart-solutions', 0, 0, 'Smart Solutions', '1970-01-01 01:01:01', '', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>In today\'s business world, outsourcing to contractors or agencies is a steady but consistent move from companies that hire permanent staff to play a key role in business. Outsourcing can be anything from catering, cleaning and maintenance to human resources, marketing and IT support. Outsourcing these key roles provides the company with huge savings, as well as a new degree of flexibility that can be used in business functions. IT support is one of the most important services for most companies, as many of them rely too much on IT services in their daily work, which were previously managed by their internal IT teams, but more and more people are enjoying the great benefits of external IT support.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The main benefit of external IT support is the cost that the company saves by hiring specialized IT technicians. Although employees have to pay technician salaries, retirement pension contributions and national insurance contributions, as well as sickness and vacation salaries, in addition to many other costs, IT outsourcing covers the same costs for outsourcing. With the company\'s IT support team, the company will have to finance the cost of any necessary equipment and provide a place to work. Many of these costs are eliminated by outsourcing IT support, as the company only has to pay for service and parts to complete any repairs or upgrades. Initially, with the help of IT support, the company incurred not only monthly expenses related to permanent employees, but also assistance costs if necessary.</p>\r\n<p>Second, companies will have the flexibility offered by IT. Working with the internal IT support team will be limited to that team and the number of people working on it, but more resources may be available with the service provider if needed. For example, day-to-day maintenance of a computer system would require much less staff than upgrading hardware or software or completing a system-wide hotfix. It would be difficult for a company to provide such an opportunity for employees, and hiring employees for such a scenario would not be effective. In contrast, external IT support can allocate more of its staff to a particular company in the event of that requires immediate attention and additional support.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to huge cost savings for businesses and a high degree of flexibility in IT support, external IT support provides a high level of knowledge and experience accumulated over a period of time by an expert contractor. This knowledge and experience is not limited to the client company, but can be gained by supporting many companies and organizations with the skills to handle many different situations. Of course, using external IT support is a smart approach to IT support, delivering these benefits, and more.</p>\r\n<h3>IMRANONLINE is a leading brand that offers smart solution with the integration of best IT custom designed software in enterprises business. We make sure that our responsive and friendly staff will be happy to serve you with the best possible IT smart solution all the time.&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', 'sibJzMzmj', 0, 0, 1, '2020-12-11 00:13:05', 0);
