(22, 'flaticon-digital-marketing-2', 'digital.jpg', 'digital', 'Web Applications', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"color: #6b6b84; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Responsive Customer Service</span>: The web development activity will involve ongoing collaboration with the website development services provider, that why it is mandatory to website development company to provide a high level of customer service.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #6b6b84; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Website development Charges</span>: The 2nd top tips for outsourcing web development services is to find out the best website development charges that perfectly meet your budget.</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #6b6b84; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Innovative and custom designed website design</span>: No matter what you use to build a website for your site, you should have basic skills and an understanding of the principles of web design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #6b6b84; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</span>: The SEO area of knowledge related to website development that you need to look for in software developer is SEO.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"color: #6b6b84; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Profile</span>: Before you contract with a web development provider, make sure you are satisfied with the quality of their previously completed projects.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 1, '2020-12-04 22:10:08');
